Class MerkleTreeNodeEntries

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.map.impl.MerkleTreeNodeEntries

    public class MerkleTreeNodeEntries
extends Object

    The map entries that belong to a specific merkle tree node. The merkle tree node is identified by the node order.
